4.4 Hyper-Parameter Study(RQ3) 

In the following part of the paper, we study the impacts of hyper-
parameters on two MaskNet models, including 1) the number of 
feature embedding size; 2) the number of MaskBlock; and 3) the 
reduction ratio in instance-guided mask module. The experiments 
are conducted on Criteo dataset via changing one hyper-parameter 
while holding the other settings. The hyper-parameter experiments 
show similar trend in other two datasets.
